Description: Based in Smithville, Tennessee, Impact Dispersal Systems, LLC offers the IDS Safety Pivot System, a unique device for Child Safety Seats.
Headquarters Regions: Southern US
Full Description: A number of applications involve a shock or impact during normal use or emergency situations. A system is needed that reduces the energy transmitted to occupant or vehicle during these high energy events. Impact Dispersal Systems, LLC has developed a patented impact dispersion system that has shown dramatic reduction in transmitted acceleration levels. The Impact Dispersal System is a new invention that takes a novel approach to reducing force from impacts. Unlike other systems, the Impact Dispersal System does not absorb the force, but disperses it away from the point of impact. The system quickly reacts, dispersing the crash energy at the point of impact and then systematically shuts down according to the amount of crash energy produced by the impact . This feature is the unique characteristic of this invention. The system has no recoil which can be important in some applications. Impact Dispersal systems received a small business innovative research (SBIR) grant from the Air Force for crashworthy stowable troop seating for helicopter topic number AF081-003. In a proof of concept test conducted by PAR3 Technology for the Air Force, the system had an 86% reduction in transmitted acceleration levels in a 60 G impact test. The system works by using variable dispersion. To give the most protection, the system would have to disperse more of the fluids at the point of impact than it does at the end of the dispersion. To accomplish this it would need different force levels, and different rates of dispersion for each level. If the force from the impact reaches the highest level, all the relief valves will open, and as the force reduces, the relief valves set at the higher level will shut down first. This would continue until all the valves shut down. After having success with the multiple valve system they thought it would be better to incorporate all these features into one valve. They designed, tested and patented a variable one piston valve that can replace the multiple valve system. They also have developed and patented a two piston valve for extreme high-energy impacts using less amount of stroke and a pressure actuating valve for the Impact Dispersal System.
Industry Groups: Energy, Government and Military, Health Care

Full Description: Law Office of Eric Harron The Law Office of Eric Harron offers legal services for a variety of cases that fall under two main categories, criminal defense and personal injury. If you have recently been charged with a misdemeanor or felony, or have been injured in an accident, Eric Harron is ready to dedicate his expertise to your case in Central Texas. Attorney Eric Harron has experience that brings results for many different personal injury and criminal defense cases. When you choose Eric Harron, you will get years of result-driven legal experience for your specific case, whether it be a criminal defense case (like DWI or drug crime) or a personal injury case (like a car accident). DWI A DWI (driving while intoxicated) charge can tarnish your criminal record and land you in jail. Being charged with a DWI, you will face two charges. The first charge is a misdemeanor and is labeled as a criminal charge. The second is a civil charge, and it pertains to whether or not you get to keep your license. This is where Eric Harron can step in to help you handle your DWI charge. Eric Harron has taken several DWI cases to court and has the experience you need to feel confident about your trial. Drug Crimes The Law Office of Eric Harron have experience with drug crimes, including possession of a controlled substance, selling illegal drugs, and possession of drug paraphernalia. Eric Harron stay current on all search and seizure laws, so he can uncover any mistakes that were made when you were searched or arrested. Personal Injury Personal service is at the core of Eric Harron's legal services. He is dedicated to personally discussing what happened in your car accident or other personal injury case, so he can be prepared to be successful in court. Many personal injury lawyers will avoid taking a case to court because of the time and expense of litigation. While settlement is an option, he has taken several cases to court if it was in my client’s best interest.  Other Criminal Defense Cases The Law Office of Eric Harron handles a variety of criminal defense cases, including animal cruelty, assault, firearms offenses, internet crimes, theft crimes, and more. You can schedule a no-cost meeting, so I can get to know you and your case personally. Pricing Mr. Harron’s fees are always upfront and reasonable. He will work to find a payment schedule that works for both parties involved. Additionally, all major credit cards are accepted.
